      "description": "Budget-friendly and honestly presented, this vehicle offers an affordable entry point for a handy driver, first-time buyer, or project-minded shopper. It shows its age and will benefit from attention, but it remains a practical opportunity for someone seeking basic transportation or a solid starting point at a very approachable price. If you value transparency and low upfront cost, this is a smart one to consider.",
