      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transport, a project, or a handy spare. It\u2019s being priced fairly for what it is, and with a little attention it could still serve someone well. If you want an honest car at an easy-to-reach price, come take a look.",
